# currentHistoryToken

**Instance Property**

The current history token.

## Declaration

```swift
var currentHistoryToken: Data? { get }
```

## Discussion

When fetching contacts or change history events, use the token on [doc://com.apple.contacts/documentation/Contacts/CNFetchResult] instead.
